Building on linux for windows target (Cross-compile)
= Build prerequisites = 
x86 or x86_64 Linux based OS (any distro and/or architecture capable of building crypto++ should work) 
Crypto++ development(header)-files Crypto++ libraries (static linking is strongly recommended) 
Compitable cross-compiler, Mingw-W64 is recommended. Use Mingw for 32-bit targets.
= Building = make all 
Is the simpliest option, it will build for all supported targets (Win,Linux,32,64,etc)
